data.description: Welcome to Colusa Sunrise Landing!  This newer construction home has everything! The open concept allows for connection while still enjoying personal space. The layout is ideal for gatherings. The focal point of the central kitchen is the enormous island with dining bar. On either side, the great room and casual dining space open out to the back yard. The downstairs bedroom with full bath is featured off the foyer. A bonus room and the huge main bedroom with en-suite including a Roman tub and shower are upstairs along with two secondary bedrooms and full bathroom; all with walk-in wardrobes. The spacious laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. Enjoy your spacious, fenced backyard and patio - ready for entertaining and picturesque Colusa sunsets!    -Seller offering up to $10,000 credit to buyer!-
